Package: endoPRS
Title: endoPRS: Incorporating endophenotype information to improve polygenic risk scores 
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Elena", "Kharitonova", , "ekhar@ad.unc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3060-3956"))
Description: This package fits a polygenic risk score using the endoPRS method. endoPRS is a weighted penalized regression model that incorporates information from endophenotypes to improve polygenic risk score prediction.
